docs.text: Open source at Thales Open Source Software & Hardware are major concerns for Thales, we want to foster collaborations between the actors of these communities through this GitHub organization . Please browse some of the projects available for further details. Contributing If you are interested to contribute to one of our projects, don't hesitate to contact us oss@thalesgroup.com
